timelineItems.name: Teshawn Edmonds
timelineItems.text: GAME ON at @RioTintoStadium: @ColoradoRapids v @RealSaltLake #RSLvCOL #RockyMountainCup

timelineItems.name: Aowabin
timelineItems.text: Good example of the directness Plata brings - two Rapids defenders easily taken out of the game there. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: Plata has touched the ball like 3 times and those three times have already been some of the brightest moments for #RSL all year. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: Close #RSL: Morales' free-kick deflects off the wall and goes just wide. Then unmarked Saborio heads over from the corner. (13) 0-0 #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Travis Cain
timelineItems.text: #RSL already with several great chances on goal. Can't wait to see what happens if we can keep up this pressure.

timelineItems.name: JP Chunga
timelineItems.text: Of the Rapids starters, Sam Cronin has the most goals scored against RSL w/ 1. #RSLvCOL http://t.co/SeTKmM4t3x

timelineItems.name: Andrea Chapman
timelineItems.text: 12' | From a corner kick, Sabo heads a ball just over the goal. Brilliant ball to Sabo, he needed to do more with it. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: Welcome back to the starting line-up @MarceloSarvas after injury. #RSLvCOL 💪💪 http://t.co/qwTEuiVnBy

timelineItems.desc: Real Salt Lake welcome the Colorado Rapids to town for a Rocky Mountain Cup clash at Rio Tinto Stadium.
timelineItems.title: HIGHLIGHTS: Real Salt Lake vs. Colorado Rapids | June 7, 2015

timelineItems.desc: MLSsoccer.com's Armchair Analyst Matt Doyle gives his take on the return of Joao Plata and how he might not be the solution to the lackluster performance of the 4-3-3 for Real Salt Lake.
timelineItems.title: Armchair Analyst: Plata not the missing puzzle piece in 4-3-3

timelineItems.name: Travis Cain
timelineItems.text: "Professional foul" and no card? #RSL

timelineItems.name: Inside MLS
timelineItems.text: Colorado has done well away from home this season. Good defensive shape. Willing to adjust and scramble. #RSL will have to break them down.

timelineItems.name: Real Salt Lake
timelineItems.text: 25' - Mulholland booked for #RSL, will be suspended next yellow

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: Mastroeni and Morales having words now. Did you guys know that this is rivalry? Fun fact. Mastroeni has done some things...#RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Mike Gavin
timelineItems.text: @ESPNFC The Stache is in the house at Rio Tinto. #RSLvCOL http://t.co/kMFRdBvZgu

timelineItems.name: Chris Kamrani
timelineItems.text: Aaron Maund is receiving instruction from defenders coach Tyrone Marshall. Don't think Olave will be back in. No clue what happened. #RSL

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray

timelineItems.name: Nathan Copier
timelineItems.text: Nice to see my displeasure of Harrington follows him from team to team #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Royal Review
timelineItems.text: Really stupid shot from about Price there by the Rapids. I'll take that all day. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.text: Too many hopeful long balls both ways right now. Ugly stuff. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids

timelineItems.text: That didn't miss by much.... #RSL

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids

timelineItems.text: Jamison Olave is down within the first couple of minutes. He's on the sideline getting treatment. May need an early change. #RSL #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Andrea Chapman
timelineItems.text: Sabo just wide, Sabo over the goal ... Sabo getting good chances. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Matthew P Ronne â
timelineItems.text: Stop playing referee, Pablo, play head coach. #Rapids96

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: .@bobbyburling's towering header forces keeper Nick Rimando to tip over. (42) 0-0 #RSLvCOL.

timelineItems.name: RSL Memes
timelineItems.text: The 4-3-3 looks good with Plata, Jaime, Morales, and Sabo. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.text: I do have eyes on Mastroeni, he didn't actually pull the fire alarm to give his team quick break. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Tim Donahoe
timelineItems.text: #RSLvCOL #RSL Pablo really needs to change something up at halftime. Rapids have been very fortunate so far.

timelineItems.text: HT RSL 0-0 Rapids. Scoreless through the 1st 45 minutes of the Rocky Mountain Cup. 15 combined shots, none on target in first half. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.text: The first half of #RSLvCOL has to be the worst half of soccer I've seen in a long time. Didn't finish #NZLvNED yesterday, so doesn't count

timelineItems.name: Sean Walker
timelineItems.text: Colorado out-fouled RSL 11-6 in the first half; Stott whistled a foul every 2.64 minutes, plus 2 yellow cards. #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Denz
timelineItems.text: Lots of chances for #RSL in first half, but 0-0 isn't a good score line for RSL The Rapids have only given up 4 goals in the 2nd half

timelineItems.text: Agonizingly close for Luke Mulholland. His header just misses the target. The win beckoned. (86'). #RSLvCOL

timelineItems.name: Tyler Gray
timelineItems.text: Mulholland's diving header is wide of the mark and we're still tied here. #RSLvCOL
